since i already have node installed i used the commands below to instal sass 
## 1 Open Command Prompt: Press Win + R, type cmd, and hit Enter.
# Install SASS
In the command prompt i run the following command:
npm install -g sass
# Verify Installation
Run the following command to ensure SASS is installed correctly:
sass --version
# Start Using SASS
compiled sass file by running
sass input.scss output.css